quran[9]{c,v,t}:
  7,179,"Gomɗii Men taganii Jahannama ko ɗuuɗi e jinna e yimɓe. Hiɓe mari ɓerɗe, ɓe faamirtaa ɗe. Hiɓe mari gite, ɓe yi'irtaa ɗe. Hiɓe mari noppi, ɓe nanirtaa ɗi. Ɓen no wa'i wa neemoraaɗi, toode ko kamɓe ɓuri majjude. Ko ɓen woni welsindiiɓe ɓen"
  7,180,"Ko Alla woodani inɗe ɓurɗe moƴƴude ɗen. Noddiree Mo ɗe, tertoɗon ɓen ooñotooɓe ka inɗe Makko : arma ɓe yoɓoyee ko ɓe gollaynoo"
  7,181,"Hino e ɓen ɓe Men tagi, mofte feewirayɗe goonga, ko ɗum kadi ɓe nunɗirta"
  7,182,"Ɓen fennuɓe Aayeeje Amen ɗen, Men suyniray ɓe e nokku ka ɓe anndaa"
  7,183,"Miɗo nennana ɓe, pellet, pewje Am ɗen ko tiiɗuɗe"
  7,184,"E ɓee miijitaaki? wonndiiɗo maɓɓe on aldaa e jinna : on wonaali si wanaa jertinoowo ɓannguɗo"
  7,185,"E ɓe ndaaraali laamuuji kammuuli ɗin e leydi ndin, e ko Alla tagi e piiji, e haawnaaki hara lajal maɓɓe ngal ɓadike? E ko yewtere honnde ɓaawo ndee ɗoo ɓe gomɗinta"
  7,186,"Kala mo Alla majjini, fewnoowo mo alaa. Himo acca ɓe e bewre maɓɓe hiɓe bumam-bumannoo"
  7,187,"Hiɓe lanndo maa fii darngal : \"ko honnde woni daragol maggal?\" Maaku : \"Anndee ganndal mun ko ka Joomi am woni. Alaa feññioowo waqtu maggal on si wanaa Kanko. Ngal teddii ka kammuuli e ka leydi. Ngal arataa e mon si wanaa e juhal\". Hiɓe lanndo maa a sikkay ko a huɓindiiɗo e ɗum. Maaku : \"Anndee ganndal mun ko ka Alla woni\". kono ko ɓuri ɗuuɗude e yimɓe ɓen anndaa [ɗum]"